  "text": "A total of 37 patients with a restenotic culprit lesion that was suitable for DCA were included. The patient cohort consisted of 18 patients with chronic stable angina, classes 1-3 according to the Canadian Cardiovascular Society (CCS) classification (8) and 19 patients with UA, classes I-III according to Braunwald's classification [CITATION_1] .",
